17572ca0aefacba","tid":828791,"uid":178102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T04:17:27.000Z","msg":"支那臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd8c984bda7176b321b92d63abeebaab39c0f40","tid":828791,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd08d0c81ad77e281b503ac622dd61ed69051fee","tid":828791,"uid":115270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:04:33.000Z","msg":"估錯地方"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T04:25:31.000Z","msg":"我以為新北"},{"pid":"d3d89f0a79be6fa44c78347a3f4ebb4dcbc41197","tid":828791,"uid":136662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T04:29:48.000Z","msg":"被告送貨到她工作店舖，店長叫她簽收，被告離開店舖後折返，問她拿電話號碼，她答應。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f16f0fffdbc82dbb91b7577d47a90deb81954af2","tid":828791,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T04:34:51.000Z","msg":"大陸妹特別多契哥契爺表哥"},{"pid":"4e2004d495df8577da175527870bbd6e8cfdadd5","tid":828791,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T07:44:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">司機涉姦女售貨員 事主認主動約被告為搜證告密</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/K8ygFZPLNtyov.p__3wgSQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/dee160309d66d1a7ca16953663aeae89\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FK8ygFZPLNtyov.p__3wgSQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fdee160309d66d1a7ca16953663aeae89&h=e5f653d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">被告羅森森否認一項強姦罪。(互聯網)</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n女事主X繼續作供，她稱被告事發前已先後3次駕車接載她去吃飯及放工。X承認是她主動相約被告於案發當晚見面，因被告經常講自己女友壞話，同時又想X做他女友，X覺得被告「為人好衰」，因此希望藉相約被告外出，趁被告講女友壞話時，用手機偷錄被告的說話，以便收集罪證向被告的女友告密，X指她可透過Instagram與被告的女友聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n控方庭上讀出事發前被告與X之間的WhatsApp對話紀錄，X向被告表示「我喜歡上了你」，還問被告「你係咪真係有鍾意我？係咪玩玩下(吓)？」被告否認「玩玩下(吓)」，X說「好啦咁就相信你一次」，之後被告說「我窮過佢(X的男友)，你介唔介意？」X答「唔介意」。另一段對話提到，被告問X：「你真係有仔(男友)？」X答「(如果)我有仔，你覺得我仲可以覆你WhatsApp、接你電話同你出去？」<br />\n<br />\nX供稱，她是為了游說被告願意外出，才在上述對話當中謊稱喜歡被告，她說自己無男友也只是謊話，她亦向被告謊稱自己辭了職，好使被告不會再到她工作的店舖找她。最終她相約被告於案發當晚8時許，在她住所樓下附近見面。<br />\n<br />\nX稱當晚被告將其客貨車停泊在路邊，被告見到她便拉開後座車門叫她上車，上車後被告關上車門，她與被告起初只是傾談及各自「撳手機」，後來被告開始摸她及吻她的臉和頸，她有叫「唔好」，但被告繼續用雙手攬她的腰，將她壓在車後座的椅子上，她嘗試推開被告但不成功，因被告太大力，之後被告便捲起她的上衣摸她的胸。X憶述案發經過時候，開始情緒激動及哭喊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E6%B6%89%E5%A7%A6%E5%A5%B3%E5%94%AE%E8%B2%A8%E5%93%A1-%E4%BA%8B%E4%B8%BB%E8%AA%8D%E4%B8%BB%E5%8B%95%E7%B4%84%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E7%82%BA%E6%90%9C%E8%AD%89%E5%91%8A%E5%AF%86-072259844.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%25A7%25A6%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%2594%25AE%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E8%25AA%258D%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25B4%2584%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E5%2591%258A%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%2590%259C%25E8%25AD%2589%25E5%2591%258A%25E5%25AF%2586-072259844.html&d=ejPMF%2FKsVkkqkU0aRqzJe4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=cea38ba1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E6%B6%89%E5%A7%A6%E5%A5%B3%E5%94%AE%E8%B2%A8%E5%93%A1-%E4%BA%8B%E4%B8%BB%E8%AA%8D%E4%B8%BB%E5%8B%95%E7%B4%84%E8%A2%AB%E5%91%8A%E7%82%BA%E6%90%9C%E8%AD%89%E5%91%8A%E5%AF%86-072259844.html</a>"},{"pid":"fe482d2994e82eba75e3d469550b0294d9502a5a","tid":828791,"uid":11598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T07:48:35.000Z","msg":"羅森森 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d70d20de4dba6b457f8b05348a06daa1fb998d","tid":828791,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T07:51:02.000Z","msg":"條大陸閪收兵r著數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f55cb1811a98e4cddcae604a6d6c6121687031","tid":828791,"uid":127347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T07:58:36.000Z","msg":"有仔仲同人食飯跟上車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e071af682932b488456d5d549d6ddc394e1e1d48","tid":828791,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T08:02:57.000Z","msg":"臭雞， 有男友仲俾機會狗公"},{"pid":"a0e2e19cf40e0af6400df25d8ef1887811f619cb","tid":828791,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T08:07:54.000Z","msg":"自己送上門既死臭雞<br />\n有男友仲坐人架車...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47464a2677bdaab3d98db7ae61607e42f1b4d5b6","tid":828791,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T08:07:59.000Z","msg":"有男朋友仲俾電話人 想收人兵啦臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e2cc645fdbe92ebb1526bb0472f7992f6878e53","tid":828791,"uid":137604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T08:13:32.000Z","msg":"啲貨灣狗搞到部車鬼五馬六原來就係想引女屌西<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}